---
title: Turkey Meatball Provencal with Spaghetti and Parmesan
description: Our spaghetti and meatballs taste just like Nonna's, but only takes a fraction of the time! The secret to these healthier meatballs is swapping ground beef for turkey and pairing with a homemade tomato sauce that keeps the dish flavorful.
